Class UnionSketchAlgebraicIntermediateFinal<S extends org.apache.datasketches.tuple.Summary>

  • java.lang.Object

  • Type Parameters:
    S - Type of Summary
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UnionDoubleSummarySketch.IntermediateFinal

    public abstract class UnionSketchAlgebraicIntermediateFinal<S extends org.apache.datasketches.tuple.Summary>
extends org.apache.pig.EvalFunc<org.apache.pig.data.Tuple>
    This is to calculate the intermediate pass (combiner) or the final pass (reducer) of an Algebraic sketch operation. This may be called multiple times (from the mapper and from the reducer). It will receive a bag of values returned by either the Intermediate or the Initial stages, so it needs to be able to differentiate between and interpret both types.
